6289 - Services Allied with the Exchange of Securities or Commodities, Not Elsewhere Classified Summary > AUSTRACLEAR SERVICES LIMITED is an Australian public company. Its operations cover services allied with the exchange of securities or commodities, not elsewhere classified. The company is a subsidiary of ASX LIMITED. The company is not involved in the import or export of goods. AUSTRACLEAR SERVICES LIMITED is headquartered in Sydney, New South Wales. It is headed by CFO & director Timothy Hogben. For the 2024 financial year, the company reported revenue of $36.88 million. Its net profit totalled $34,000. AUSTRACLEAR SERVICES LIMITED forms part of the finance, insurance, and real estate industry sector.
